@startuml State_Conversation
title Conversation Phase - State Diagram

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<positive>> #90EE90
    BackgroundColor<<negative>> #FFB6C1
}

[*] --> Opening

Opening : Agent greets provider rep
Opening : States purpose of call
Opening --> IdentityVerification : repAsksForVerification

IdentityVerification : Provides account number
IdentityVerification : Confirms name, ZIP, last4
IdentityVerification --> ProblemStatement : identityConfirmed
IdentityVerification --> Rejection <<negative>> : verificationFailed

ProblemStatement : "My bill is too high"
ProblemStatement : Cites competitor pricing
ProblemStatement : References loyalty tenure
ProblemStatement --> Negotiating : repEngages

Negotiating : Presents leverage points
Negotiating : Requests specific discount
Negotiating --> CounterOffer : repMakesOffer
Negotiating --> Escalation : repRefusesToNegotiate

CounterOffer : Evaluates offer terms
CounterOffer : Compares to target savings
CounterOffer --> Acceptance <<positive>> : offerAcceptable
CounterOffer --> Negotiating : counterWithHigherAsk
CounterOffer --> Escalation : belowMinimum

Escalation : Requests supervisor
Escalation : Asks for retention dept
Escalation --> Negotiating : supervisorConnected
Escalation --> Rejection <<negative>> : escalationDenied

Acceptance <<positive>> : Confirms new rate
Acceptance : Requests confirmation number
Acceptance --> WrapUp : detailsConfirmed

Rejection <<negative>> : Thanks rep for time
Rejection : Declines to proceed
Rejection --> WrapUp : closingRemarks

WrapUp : Summarizes agreed changes
WrapUp : Confirms effective date
WrapUp --> [*] : callEnds

@enduml
